measurements.description: Two flowers and one emerging flower on one 43-cm arched inflorescence; sepals pale chartreuse, veined and spotted dark cordovan; petals light chartreuse, spotted and striped dark cordovan, suffused pink into dark maroon apical seven-eights, hirsute margins; pouch light green overlaid medium cordovan; staminode light cordovan overlaid rose-brown;; substance medium; texture matte.
